snippet.title: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description:
Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League, from Rocksteady, got an all new trailer during the 2022 Game Awards, showing off the whole team together facing off against Batman, which also pays tribute to the late great Kevin Conroy who passed away earlier this year. It is expected to release May 26, 2023.

#SuicideSquad #Batman #TheGameAwards
